{"tid":506594,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人食過呢隻新嘅韓國雙重芝士撈麵","createTime":"2017-12-22T11:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T14:15:46.000Z","uid":139613,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a09b71cdfd670079f3c36f357bde9c66276e8b","tid":506594,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/185919_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F185919_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=a7607e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚期待 一落水已經聞到個麵餅已經有陣火腿香味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 15蚊處女價食一次都算ok<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/190425_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F190425_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=b9964ccb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52083d1bd40e42edcd8722e10fdbd0b3f471b1cf","tid":506594,"uid":139613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"哇屌好撚淡 好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落太多水了"},{"pid":"e01dacf31b22f00c6f432d6a0cdbc25a25cea9e4","tid":506594,"uid":38030,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"撈面唔係應該倒哂啲水先落粉咩，你做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d9aa2e5e648ddb256a4a6ce959784768d3e3ad","tid":506594,"uid":139613,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撈面唔係應該倒哂啲水先落粉咩，你做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一開始以為撈麵 跟住睇真啲封面有湯嘅屌<br />\n但佢又冇水線 唯有就咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d423fcb153aee0882245568ea4ef3317a9924b